    "Designed to challenge LLMs in factual accuracy, reasoning, and understanding of complex contexts Specificity for Hallucination Tasks included to specifically address and measure the model's proneness to hallucination -Necessity: This metric is critical for evaluating the effectiveness of the integration strategy, ensuring that the real-time data accessed through the API genuinely enhances the model's output.Such comprehensive evaluation criteria were designed to provide a holistic view of the model's improvements post-integration, focusing on both qualitative and quantitative aspects of performance enhancement.",
